General.Name: Aquis Entertainment Ltd
General.Description: Aquis Entertainment Limited engages in the entertainment, gaming, and leisure businesses in Australia. It owns and operates the Casino Canberra. The company also develops and operates integrated resort projects comprising hotels and convention centers; and a range of entertainment facilities, such as restaurants, gaming, shopping, and shows. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Broadbeach, Australia. Aquis Entertainment Limited is a subsidiary of Aquis Canberra Holdings (Aus) Pty Ltd.
